PROMPT oracle_bone_dating_shang
WITH BUDGET 6000 tokens
USING MODEL "claude-sonnet-4-5"

SELECT
    system_role("You are a Chinese archaeology and historical chronology expert specializing in Shang dynasty historiography, oracle bone paleography, and the methodologies used to establish historical dating through ancient Chinese inscriptions.")

GENERATE
    explain_dating_methods("Explain how oracle bone script helps historians date events in the Shang Dynasty. Cover: 1) The stratigraphic dating method where oracle bones found in specific archaeological layers at Yinxu can be correlated with particular time periods and royal reigns, 2) Paleographic analysis showing how oracle bone character forms evolved over time, allowing scholars to establish relative chronological sequences based on script style changes, 3) The identification of specific Shang kings mentioned in oracle bone inscriptions and how this connects to the traditional king lists in later historical texts like the Shiji, enabling absolute dating, 4) Cross-referencing of astronomical events recorded on oracle bones (eclipses, planetary conjunctions, seasonal observations) with modern astronomical calculations to establish precise dates, 5) The carbon-14 dating of organic materials (bone, wood, charcoal) found in the same archaeological contexts as oracle bones to provide scientific chronological anchors, 6) How oracle bone inscriptions record specific historical events (military campaigns, royal ceremonies, natural disasters) that can be correlated with archaeological evidence and environmental data, 7) The use of oracle bone genealogical information to reconstruct Shang royal succession and establish reign periods for individual kings, 8) How the content and language evolution in oracle bone texts reflects broader historical and cultural changes within Shang society over time, 9) The integration of oracle bone chronological data with bronze inscription dates to create a more comprehensive Shang dynasty timeline, 10) The limitations and challenges in oracle bone dating, including the fragmentary nature of many inscriptions and the ongoing scholarly debates about absolute chronology, 11) Specific examples of key dated oracle bone discoveries and how they have refined our understanding of Shang dynasty chronology.")
WITH OUTPUT BUDGET 3000 tokens, TEMPERATURE 0.1, FORMAT markdown;